Description: MedLEA contains a dataset of morphological and structural features of Medicibal LEAves (MedLEA). The features of each species is recorded by manually viewing the medicinal plant repository available at \url{http://www.instituteofayurveda.org/plants/}. The package also provides a link to download leaf images of 1099 medicinal plants in Sri Lanka.
